== Overview ==

dkAntispamPlugin is a simple plugin to allow any symfony application to give a
"spam note" to any text. No more p3n1s 3nlarg3rs will damage your nice website.

== Install ==

To check it out:

{{{
svn co http://svn.symfony-project.com/plugins/dkAntispamPlugin/trunk
}}}

To use it as an external:
{{{
svn propedit svn:externals plugins

dkAntispamPlugin http://svn.symfony-project.com/plugins/dkAntispamPlugin/trunk
}}}

